{"word":"εἰσδρομή","slug":"εἰσδρομή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>εἰσδρομή</b></el> <el>(εἰσδρομή, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>εἰσδράμεῖν</el>, aor2 <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> of <a href='S:εἰστρέχω'><el>εἰστρέχω</el></a>\n<p/><i>an inroad, onslaught</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/>"}]}